    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jester's Spooktacular DLC</strong><br>Prepare for a spine-chilling adventure in the newest <i>Dungeon Defenders</i> DLC, <i>Jester's Spooktacular</i>! Enter a haunting reskin of the iconic Jester's Board map with a new boss, new loot, and more</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Included in the DLC:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jester's Spooktacular Map</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss - Flying Pumpkin</strong><i> - The secret to an encounter with this foe is through the unusual tiles.</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Punk Jester Skin</strong> - <i>Earned on map completion</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Weapons</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Corrupted Axe </strong>- <i>Earned on map completion</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dragon Halberd </strong>- <i>Earned on map completion</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Accessory:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Devil Mask</strong> - <i>Earned on map completion</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Pet:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flying Pumpkin Pet</strong> - <i>Earned on map completion after beating Flying Pumpkin Boss</i></p></li></ul></li></ul>",
